cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper uses computer vision techniques to analyze satellite imagery for road quality monitoring. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses machine learning algorithms, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of neural networks for classification tasks makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also deals with transportation infrastructure, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics).
